{"tid":1550932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有今日大埔墟黑警圍捕嘅片清晰版？","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:05:32.000Z","uid":153689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93e7752578810395e0a252dc721f72a64768d09a","tid":1550932,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"頭先睇到發現有個人好似我個frd，但又聯絡唔到<br />\n想睇真啲係咪我朋友，但啲片都好濛<br />\n想知有冇人/知邊到有高清版？"},{"pid":"12b13c8d0e514165e230fa130451f3b972c2f94d","tid":1550932,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:47:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74a59445a9b37feff6b875ffab4f9f4cbec1b744","tid":1550932,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:48:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faf17216aee99684e3c53c75581289a2ed1b5f0b","tid":1550932,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:48:24.000Z","msg":"612"},{"pid":"a93ea717adb1ec580ef054c0d662b7987cdb7d94","tid":1550932,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:48:52.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"25eccf9a74bc718edc717