re,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n今日見！</span>"},{"pid":"f167244b72d763442e497e76730dcbd5a14e717f","tid":1550932,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:50:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8075461ac50ea7f72933e757c184be9300a5952","tid":1550932,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:50:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bf5362fe803fcd45794126cacf2b8bcfc87bdfd","tid":1550932,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:01:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d69caa9276e7e793a5a5482d5988bbd140b431a","tid":1550932,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:03:46.000Z","msg":"Icable fb"},{"pid":"3e6190c04ade53095889dabd1095532e644b80f0","tid":1550932,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:17:12.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"99cd25958c7d9e3a705443a79e9d25d8a10c3c81","tid":1550932,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}